{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also had a piece of bread and something with it very often, like a piece of margarine or a-- or a little bit of jam, and sometimes even a piece of sausage, but always of the lowest variety.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were always rejects from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, they meant life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working on the railroad, as well, in transport, mainly loading and unloading of freight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father was with the locomotive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This has a meaning because this contributed to our survival.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, before I answer your question, being on the hunger and survival, we saw many people, particularly those with good appetites, starving rapidly of hunger and dying.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many-- I see a number of them before my eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So getting some food some way was a life-saving-- was a life-saving event.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who had-- who were geared towards eating, and so, who suffered enormously from hunger, they succumbed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I saw a lot of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You asked the question, what--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Russians came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the Russians came closer, the Germans had to liquidate the camps and run west.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was now in Skarzysko, and when Skarzysko was liquidated, we were sent to Buchenwald, which is already in Germany, close to Weimar.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you a date, but I can tell you it's 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The best I remember is I was not cold in Buchenwald, and so it must have been-- it was not winter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 1944, probably spring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot-- I cannot be sure, but it was at the time of the Polish uprising in Russia, because people from that uprising were brought to Buchenwald together with us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a nice story there at Buchenwald that I may want to tell you.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
